  "text": "For the quantification of clustered vesicles, we included vesicles located within the range of 250 nm away from a T-bar (AZ), as performed previously [CITATION_1] . For the quantification of docked vesicles, we included vesicles that surround the T-bar (250 nm) and are 30 nm away from the plasma membrane.",
